name: Spaced Out! (LOCKDOWNLOSER)
description:
SPACED OUT

A little diversion in the hellscape that is the unforeseen circumstances.

The object of this game is to advance, and clear the obstacles.

As you advance through glitched backgrounds, nostalgic music, and tight gaps, you may start to realize that there is a lack of content. Well, that's because this is only version 1 of many.
